  "texts": [
    "ChatGPT helps in structuring objectives and designing methodologies, while students continuously review and refine their proposals based on the system's suggestions, enhancing their skills in academic writing and the development of research questions.For data analysis and interpretation, students leverage ChatGPT to analyze their research data, identify patterns, and draw meaningful conclusions.",
    "This activity fosters competencies in data analysis, critical thinking, and information synthesis.",
    "Students input their data into ChatGPT, which generates insights and identifies key patterns.",
    "The students then evaluate the generated analysis critically, integrating the results into their own research findings, thus refining their ability to process and interpret data.In conducting a collaborative literature review, ChatGPT assists students in gathering and summarizing relevant sources on a given topic.",
    "Students specify the topic, and ChatGPT provides key summaries and points from relevant literature."
